        public void addAdjacentNode​(Node node,

        Parameters:
        node - The adjacent node to add.
        weight - The weight (distance) to the adjacent node.

      • calcProvideScore

        public void calcProvideScore​(java.lang.Double maxDis,
                             java.lang.Double maxSource,
                             java.lang.Double maxStorage,
                             java.lang.Double maxConsumption)
        Calculates the provide and consumption scores for this node. The scores are based on the node's energy capacities, consumption, distance, and weighting factors.
        Parameters:
        maxDis - The maximum distance in the network.
        maxSource - The maximum energy source capacity in the network.
        maxStorage - The maximum energy storage capacity in the network.
        maxConsumption - The maximum energy consumption in the network.
